text: Aun Abbas (born 15 June 1998) is a Pakistani cricketer. He made his List A debut on 20 January 2017 for Islamabad in the 2016–17 Regional One Day Cup. He made his first-class debut for Zarai Taraqiati Bank Limited in the 2018–19 Quaid-e-Azam Trophy on 25 September 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Islamabad cricketers Category:Zarai Taraqiati Bank Limited cricketers Category:Cricketers from Faisalabad
